                <h1 class="title">Hi! My name is<n class="name ml-2"style="color: #4169E1;">Arnold</n>,</h1>
                <h2 class="subtitle py-1">I am a Junior Software Developer.</h2>
            </div>
            <a class="btn btn-outline-primary text-capitalize touch" href="#reachout">get in touch</a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!--End Landing Page-->
  <!--Start intro about me-->
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-8">
            <div class="title-intro">
                <h2 class="text-lead text-capitalize">a brief intro about what i do</h2>
                <p>I am a developer who enjoys turning ideas into reality. I specialize in database driven applications, using various technologies such <strong>Java </strong> and <strong class="text-primary"> ASP.Net Core</strong></p>
